01 is the snake layer
11 is snake layer width
21 is snake layer height
31 is window layer
41 is the response layer
51 is the response x
61 is the response y
71 is the snake length
81 is the window width
91 is the window height
a1 is the 'in use' marker
b1 is the color white
c1 is the 'redraw all' marker - otherwise ignores middle of snake
